			<h5 class="case-study-title">Our Solution</h5>
		</div>
		<div class="pull-right big-block">
			<p>
				Tap to Fund fixes this problem by providing a single place, on your mobile phone, where you can discover and search for charities or institutions and do the whole process with the simplicity of a few clicks. Users will see a smart feed with charities of their interest or geographically close to them. They can also search for a specific charity by name or type. Users can use a credit card to donate automatically and monthly to all of the organizations of their choosing. Greatly simplifying the process of giving back to the world, even if it’s just a couple of dollars a month.
			</p>
