		</div>
		<div class="pull-right big-block">
			<p>
				Luckily for us, for this project, we took part on naming it. So once we started working on the brand, we seeked to represent the essence of the product; “Tap to Fund”. We wanted to set really clearly that it was as easy and quick as tapping your screen to help out the organizations of your choosing.
			</p>
			<p>
				This was the starting point for the final outcome. On one hand, we found a lot of ways to represent “money” “donation” and the most important one “touch” step that is the most import part of the app. On the other hand we didn’t wanted to make it about the money but more about the action you were doing as a user. We came with a few simple proposals with one concept in mind: “one simple touch”.
			</p>
			<p>
				At the end we got a simple but at the same time a very complex proposal. An icon that represents many things at the same time. A fingertip, which is that is the main trigger now on day to control all devices, and to access all information. As well a fingerprint give the sense of the individuality. Making YOUR fingerprint the one making the difference in the cause of YOUR pick.
			</p>
